{"tid":489431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆思想好守舊...","createTime":"2017-12-04T16:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T16:49:48.000Z","uid":147603,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"00f6178a27180cad210e32e4ebd07d07cf12bb45","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:13:29.000Z","msg":"交代返少少背景先<br />\n老豆今年50幾歲<br />\n教育水平係大陸初中畢業<br />\n由於工作關係<br />\n平時接觸嘅都係同佢差唔多年紀同教育水平嘅人<br />\n除左用whatsapp做通訊工具 唔識上網<br />\n所以佢對世界嘅認知都係黎自互動新聞台<br />\n或者係同飲早茶嘅同事/朋友傾計得返黎<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我想試下染髮（唔係誇張色）<br />\n但佢對染髮非常反感<br />\n覺得染髮嘅就係飛仔飛女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到明話唔比我染髮<br />\n另外<br />\n就係有時會同朋友去海濱吹水飲酒<br />\n佢唔明我點解要去海濱到12點幾先返屋企<br />\n佢仲好唔鍾意人飲酒作樂<br />\n所以我到而家係佢面前都係扮緊一個未飲過酒、亦都無興趣飲嘅小朋友...<br />\n最後<br />\n每次同佢出去食飯都係食中餐<br />\n啫係三餸一湯加兩碗白飯咁<br />\n試過帶佢去食譚仔、吉野家邊爐、元氣<br />\n佢都好似無乜興趣咁<br />\n搞到我都覺得掃興<br />\n<br />\n有時見到身邊啲朋友同屋企人去BBQ、食pizza會覺得好warm<br />\n有少少羨慕（？）<br />\n我都想同我老豆一齊享受呢份喜悅<br />\n但佢對於新事物都幾抗拒<br />\n想問呢到有無巴絲屋企人都係咁守舊？<br />\n你地嘅情況又係點？<br />\n你地覺得可以點樣解決？<br />\n定係做個孝順嘅晚輩就下佢算？<br />\n<br />\n利申：成年人"},{"pid":"40734f736b253b619fcd62ca487c30f6fa782d29","tid":489431,"uid":90045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"18歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8604d1098de88c35920e202439dcb577e169b40c","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"希望你地唔好too long didn&rsquo;t read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知篇文係長 係1999<br />\n但真心想求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfdef999edc3e2c9fbd7a9e6658f6f6601fc165","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>18歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6d690001e16c0e52a7cc1affe221aaaa4c97a6","tid":489431,"uid":71217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"以前老豆都係咁<br />\n但係阿媽諗法比較開放<br />\n久而久之阿媽改變左佢<br />\n從此變得正常"},{"pid":"fd1f6140c657684fcda8ece23c6c54a8e1aed370","tid":489431,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"帶佢去旅行"},{"pid":"c103842607c392ecbc4a6a330abd43656ffab372","tid":489431,"uid":40337,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁點呀<br />\n等佢瓜柴囉<br />\n少啲接觸囉<br />\n對佢黎講要佢改變根本無value<br />\n改唔到架啦"},{"pid":"f8a7f6217115eda6cd30d3d0d16bed717b22bc5f","tid":489431,"uid":69719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baaf9e190ae0d3910b4185a76c4b4ac8870cf29","tid":489431,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"不過你都係睇撚住佢好啲<br />\n陣間on99買埋啲咩MBI 虛擬貨幣<br />\n臨老唔過得世"},{"pid":"4086d7abca9d7937c21631d8ff14a4b999a739aa","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前老豆都係咁<br />\n但係阿媽諗法比較開放<br />\n久而久之阿媽改變左佢<br />\n從此變得正常</blockquote><br />\n我屋企係單親家庭<br />\n老豆2年幾前開始有個40幾歲嘅女朋友<br />\n佢女朋友算係半個知識分子<br />\n外國讀書返黎香港做嘢<br />\n思想都叫做比較開放<br />\n希望佢可以改變到我阿爸啦<br />\n其實有一年老豆生日<br />\n佢女朋友book左間餐廳<br />\n我地3個一齊食西餐慶祝<br />\n之後到我生日<br />\n佢女朋友帶我地去食日本嘢<br />\n（因為我鍾意食日本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但老豆好似都唔係幾欣賞咁<br />\n有時我都好驚佢地嘅差異咁大會好易分手<br />\n我發過幾次夢都係佢地唔夾要分開<br />\n嚇到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想老豆有個人陪住 想佢幸福"},{"pid":"32f9a200ac6d8e290faa94900ce9d784c702352f","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶佢去旅行</blockquote><br />\n呢個唔錯喎！<br />\n等我睇下呢個聖誕有咩團報下先<br />\nThanks bro~"},{"pid":"d8aa40d29f354b3d1a8449fbe1b9a7fc10933dc7","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點呀<br />\n等佢瓜柴囉<br />\n少啲接觸囉<br />\n對佢黎講要佢改變根本無value<br />\n改唔到架啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁衰啦<br />\n我好鍾意我老豆架...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408173880efbe410914f0e8a4f4615583aab5560","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過你都係睇撚住佢好啲<br />\n陣間on99買埋啲咩MBI 虛擬貨幣<br />\n臨老唔過得世</blockquote><br />\n咁呢個佢又唔會<br />\n因為佢係守舊到唔會玩呢啲投機遊戲嘅人<br />\n覺得人要腳踏實地 靠自己勞力去搵食<br />\n頂多星期日賭下馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1efcf6405ef39769459a8cafdb2e950b65a4253","tid":489431,"uid":161421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"絲？老豆係會緊張啲<br />\n<br />\n不過底線係用嚟超越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咁聽話，佢緊係乜都唔比<br />\n我老豆都會咒我染髮生癌死，咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，三張嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a9be7479aa3aa0bb2025f7326b6a278a6f2695","tid":489431,"uid":36379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"我14歲開始跟老豆飲酒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea0c311032fd084b8e78ca946af97901f8ce719","tid":489431,"uid":147603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"（離題）點解要負評曬我啲comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02848950723c26643e4f4f308bf5309d01203fa","tid":489431